Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.03,0:00:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤格特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.41,0:00:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當這個大陸遭遇前所未有的危機時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.16,0:00:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個無名戰士站了出來 成立了義勇軍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.52,0:00:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼還執迷不悟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.02,0:00:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界注定要走向滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受命運吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.53,0:00:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.66,0:00:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管他是命運還是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決定這件事的人不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.42,0:00:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是生活在這個世界的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奪回這座城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:00:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:00:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.89,0:01:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的反抗是得不到任何救贖的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.02,0:01:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.73,0:01:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.36,0:01:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不會放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.11,0:01:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無聊至極
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.12,0:01:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是些雜魚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.29,0:01:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾蕾努斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.75,0:01:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來做妳的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.13,0:01:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎值得期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸裂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:02:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還沒破壞夠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直就像反派說的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.79,0:02:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眾將士們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.96,0:02:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大展我鬼族雄威吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就憑你那麼點魔力能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.01,0:02:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能抓住我們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.18,0:02:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未來的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.61,0:02:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他做到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把鎖鏈編年史和精靈交出來吧 菲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 讓這個世界結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰會交給你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.32,0:03:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精靈啊 世界意志的碎片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.66,0:03:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你就是希望和光明的象徵的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比利卡...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不得不死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該結束的是你 黑之王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤莉安娜殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖王女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕不會辜負吾父聖王和那些犧牲的士兵的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:03:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那邊看著就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就會結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰會放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲娜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比利卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比利卡她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊 黑色因子在不斷增強
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲娜 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界終將歸於黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久 尤格特大陸就會沉睡在黑暗中了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個小鬼 失敗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比利卡她 消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們失去了世界的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:58.89,title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1680,880)\blur6\fade(150,150)}光與暗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲娜小姐 我們換一下班吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再這樣下去 連妳都會倒下的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 我沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑之王討伐戰失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我們聖騎士團為首締結的尤格特同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將會依照約定解散
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都將先返回各自的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑之王的力量遠超過我們的預想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且尤里現在也成了那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:08:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重整旗鼓還需要一定的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:08:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤莉安娜殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私以為這次的作戰本就過於草率
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕在下直言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討伐黑之王 對一介散兵的尤里來說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,負擔太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意你的語氣 布爾克哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 你的心情我也能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我們把一切都賭在了尤里和義勇軍上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在尤格特大陸身處困境之時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓萬眾結為一心的正是他們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以大家把希望寄託在他們的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 上位者要有戰略和能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑之軍團不是光靠戰略和能力就能戰勝的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此 就更應該讓尤莉安娜殿下來主持大局
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被殺父之仇束縛住的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒能完成大任
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而把我從執念中解放出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是別人 正是尤里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再繼續待下去也毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班師回朝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們接下來該如何是好 首領
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,韋恩 我先率聖騎士團返回聖都
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤莉安娜殿下還是堅持留下與義勇軍共同行動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.22,0:10:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來 我也想留下一些守衛的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但現實是 根本沒有多餘的士兵可用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說 只有我和阿雷斯 布爾克哈克你不放心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是一直如此嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:11:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤莉安娜殿下的安危 就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 總帥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤里你一直都不醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易才逃到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不知道 接下來該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鎖鏈編年史 還有比利卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:02.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在只要你活著我就滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去通知大家你醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體已經痊癒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要再休息一陣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逞強到最後可是會扯後腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想先回去副都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 再集結一次戰力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想先回去副都 向吉魯伯特報告一下傷亡情況
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟公會也犧牲了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界終將歸於黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界終將歸於黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,世界終將歸於黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就妳那幾個破銅板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.79,0:13:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那至少請給我一個蘋果也好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擋路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一籃我都要了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您願意買下一整籃當然好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩枚金幣應該夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.56,0:13:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收您金幣兩枚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過最近物價真是飛漲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必窮人過得也更加困難了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那個胖子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你的腳拿開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說拿開你那髒腳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟敢對本大爺動手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟敢耍我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 我拿走了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰才是真的壞人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒有欺凌弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴白痴 超級大白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我只要一個就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你家人的份呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我一個人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我請你吃點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們還有臉這麼悠哉地回城嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的土地呢 你要怎麼賠我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 我們是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們說過的吧 說要打倒黑之王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們說過要保護我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而那卻是現在這副...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.45,0:17:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這副...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫我們今後怎麼生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:17:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是黑之軍團
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不快點的話 那些黑霧就要...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界終將歸於黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.62,0:18:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:22.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米希迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆妳快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.28,0:18:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔力很微弱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.68,0:19:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這煙霧的原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.61,0:19:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界終將歸於黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界注定要走向滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受命運吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不會放棄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口氣解決他們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 還有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的魔力給...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住未來的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是義勇軍的 尤里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.63,0:21:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.76,0:22:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是 阿蘭姆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.65,0:23:39.60,title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1130,690)\blur6}共存之事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.88,0:23:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,命運之輪開始轉動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:29.60,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}掙脫天命 這是我的解放
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:55.87,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}已然乾枯的淚水 遠方潛伏的境界線
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:07:01.30,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}全部消失吧 那些搖擺不定的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:03.95,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}明天我仍會挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:06.59,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}這永不結束的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:08.86,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}我會將羈絆緊緊連接
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:11.44,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}我會去伸手捕捉那榮光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:19.25,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}直到毀掉這未來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:23.73,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}釋放人生 撕裂靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:26.55,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}天命難違 殺出重圍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:31.48,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}多少次破碎的心靈 腐朽的靈魂重生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:34.09,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}回溯時間 重複的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:36.74,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}反擊痛苦 甦醒的本能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:41.56,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}在多少次燃燒之後的灰燼之上矗立的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:47.11,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}掙脫天命 這是我的解放
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:29.60,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}天命を振り解いて THIS IS MY LIBERATION
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:55.87,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}乾いた涙　滲む境界線
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:07:01.30,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}かき消され　揺れ惑う感情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:03.95,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}僕らは明日も独りの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:06.59,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}戦いに永遠と挑んで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:08.86,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}絆を繋いで (I WILL)　
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:11.44,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}栄光を掴んで (GO ON)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:19.25,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}この未来が　滅びてしまうくらいなら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:23.73,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}UNCHAIN YOUR LIFE　魂引き裂いて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:26.55,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}UNBREAK DESTINY を切り開いて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:31.48,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}何度心敗れ　朽ち果てたこの SOUL を再生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:34.09,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}TURN BACK THE TIME　繰り返す幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:36.74,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}FIGHT BACK THE PAIN　蘇る本能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:41.56,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}何度燃え尽くされ　その灰から立ち上がる人生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:47.11,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}天命を振り解いて THIS IS MY LIBERATION
